                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-191" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS SIMPSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in the office on this day—there was no one there but me and the prisoner—about three quarters of an hour after Mr. Greenwood went out I saw the prisoner at the desk—I said if Mr. Green<lb></lb>wood was to come in he would not like to see, him at his desk—he went out shortly after, taking his cloak with him.</p>
